## Tests

Add `*_test.go` for GAQL validation, query building, pagination, field-service parsing, and input parsers. Run:

```bash
go test ./internal/provider/googleads/...
```

CI: `.github/workflows/test.yml`.

## UI catalog sync

After adding a tool, update mcp-ads-manager `apps/web/lib/mcp-provider-tools.ts` (`ProviderAgentToolsCollapsible` on `/connections`).
